      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גולגולת תנן: <b>אידך.</b> לא גירד עדיין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 52a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תיבעי לך: <b>ששה</b> <b>דברים.</b> לקמן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 52a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קחשיב להו: <b>של</b> <b>טרסיים.</b> צורפי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 52a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נחשת ואמרי לה של אותה אומה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 52a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
